OL,3,CMan who died after train crash was
OL,4,Cidentified by his wife, inquest hears
OL,6,FA man who died when two trains
OL,7,Fcollided in mid-Wales was identified
OL,8,Fby his wife at the scene, an inquest
OL,9,Fhas heard.
OL,11,FPassenger David Tudor Evans, 66, died
OL,12,Fafter two Transport for Wales (TfW)
OL,13,Ftrains collided head-on near Talerddig
OL,14,Fin Powys at 7.26pm on 21 October.
OL,16,FWhile no official cause of death has
OL,17,Fbeen revealed, it is suspected he died
OL,18,Ffrom a heart attack.
