OL,3,CMan who died after train crash was
OL,4,Cidentified by his wife, inquest hears
OL,6,FLouisa Corcoran, assistant coroner for
OL,7,FCeredigion, opened an inquest into his
OL,8,Fdeath at the Aberystwyth Justice
OL,9,FCentre on Wednesday, 30 October.
OL,11,FThe coroner's officer said Mr Evans'
OL,12,Fwife, Rachel Evans, identified him to
OL,13,Fpolice at the scene.
OL,15,FHe said: "Mr Evans was identified at
OL,16,Fthe scene by his wife to British
OL,17,FTransport Police officers as David
OL,18,FTudor Evans from Capel Dewi."
