OL,3,CMan who died after train crash was
OL,4,Cidentified by his wife, inquest hears
OL,6,FThe coroner said a post-mortem
OL,7,Fexamination is in progress and
OL,8,Fadjourned the inquest while the police
OL,9,Finvestigation was ongoing.
OL,11,FMs Corcoran said: "Although I would
OL,12,Flike to set a date for a future
OL,13,Finquest I can't at the moment, but the
OL,14,Fdate will be set in due course."
OL,16,FFour other people suffered serious
OL,17,Finjuries during the incident, and a
OL,18,Ffurther 11 sustained injuries
OL,19,Frequiring hospital treatment.
