OL,3,CMan who died after train crash was
OL,4,Cidentified by his wife, inquest hears
OL,6,FAn internal log of what happened
OL,7,Fduring the crash shows the driver of
OL,8,Fthe train for Aberystwyth reported
OL,9,Fthey entered the loop as planned but
OL,10,Fwere "unable to stop due to the
OL,11,Frailhead conditions", causing the
OL,12,Ftrain to pass a stop signal.
OL,14,FA signaller instructed the oncoming
OL,15,Ftrain to perform an "immediate stop",
OL,16,Fbut a collision could not be avoided.
